<div class="article__content article-richedit-content">
        <p><span style="font-size: 3px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 3px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">札幌（Sapporo）</span></strong></span></p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 3px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">一个位于日本</span></span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">北海道道央地区的都会城市，为全日本人口第五多的城市，也是日本的政令指定都市之一。由于札幌市是北海道政府（道厅）以及石狩支厅办公室所在地，因此也成为北海道的行政中枢。</span></p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">除了是北海道的行政中心外，札幌也是北海道的工商业中心，曾在1972年举办过第11届冬季奥林匹克运动会；位于市中心的带状公园大通公园也是每年札幌雪祭的举办场地，因此札幌也是个国际知名的观光都市。</span></p>
<p><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-182-0.jpg" style="width: 700px; height: 556px;" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_0" width="700" height="556" border="0" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_0"></p>
<p><br></p>
<p><span style="font-size: 3px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; white-space: normal; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; text-decoration: none; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">下面就跟着大鱼君一起去札幌吃美食吧~</span></strong></span><br></p>
<p><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.2000007629395px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）之札幌拉面共和国(Sapporo ramen kyowakoku)</span></strong></span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">位于札幌站前的购物大厦ESTA的10层，北海道内味道出名的拉面店汇集一堂，是可以享受各种店铺各种拉面的主题公园。以被称为北海道四大拉面的札幌、旭川、函馆、钏路为中心，由8家名店构成。设施内再现了1945至55年代的札幌街景，充满怀旧气氛，还配有蒸汽机车、木造车站、神社等。广场内集合了8间目前北海道最高人气的拉面名店，如札幌白桦山庄、函馆あじさい、旭川梅光轩、江别银波露等。</span></p>
<p><span style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-182-1.jpg" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_1" style="white-space: normal; float: none;" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_1"></span></p>
<p><span style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">地址：北海道札幌市中央区北5西2-1 ESTA10层<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">交通：从JR札幌站的东检票口步行5分钟。从市营地铁南北线、东丰线的札幌站步行5分钟。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.2000007629395px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）之拉面横丁（Rāmen Yokochō）</span></strong></span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">位于札幌市中心的薄野，其实只是一条数十米的小巷，却有超过家拉面店，根本没有其他店铺。它存在已有30年历史，从原本的7、8家拉面店以及数间酒家发展起来，后来逐渐变成拉面店聚集的专门街。大多数拉面店的座位都不超过10人，虽然空间较为局促，但可以近距离的体会拉面师傅细心的料理功夫。</span></p>
<p><span style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-182-2.jpg" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_2" width="700" height="526" border="0" style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-weight: bold; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; width: 700px; height: 526px;" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_2"></span></p>
<p><span style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">地址:札幌市中央区南5西3<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.2000007629395px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）之螃蟹本家(札幌站前总店 )</span></strong></span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">制作螃蟹肉生鱼片、水煮螃蟹，特别讲究螃蟹肉的鲜味，因此原材料取自北海道苫小牧渔港海水循环式鱼塘中、以鲜活状态包装的新鲜活螃蟹，直接运送至日本各地的店铺，北海道外的店铺则采用空运。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">采用新鲜材料，烹调出令您心荡神驰的美味料理，全凭这些身怀绝技的日式料理专业厨师。店铺建筑采用独特的设计，以使客人能够充分品味螃蟹本家独创的美味螃蟹肉料理。<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-182-3.jpg" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_3" style="white-space: normal; float: none;" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_3"></span></p>
<p><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">地址：日本札幌北海道札幌站前总店<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.2000007629395px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）之成吉思汗达摩本店（Jingisukan daruma honten）</span></strong></span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">是札幌一家有60年历史的老店，闻名全日本的成吉思汗烤肉就是源自于此。该店选用只出生一年的小羊肉，用祖传秘方将羊肉的腥膻味去除，只留下羊肉的鲜嫩甜美。</span></p>
<p><span style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-182-4.jpg" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_4" style="white-space: normal; float: none;" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_4"></span></p>
<p><span style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">地址：札幌市中央区南5条西，4丁目，野口大楼1楼<br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);"><strong style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(0, 100, 0); font-family: Verdana, Arial; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><span style="box-sizing: border-box; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); line-height: 25.2000007629395px; font-size: 16px; background-color: rgb(84, 141, 212);">日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）之札幌甜点</span></strong></span><span style="color: rgb(127, 127, 127); font-size: 16px; word-wrap: break-word; font-family: 微软雅黑; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><br style="word-wrap: break-word; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: Tahoma, Simsun; font-size: 14px; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">2006年起，札幌当局大力推展札幌甜点，并举行年度大评选，每年评选出的代表甜点，可以在国铁札幌站西侧大厅北口的〝食与观光〞情报馆附设的甜品店〝Cafe Norte Sapporo〞（カフェノルテサッポロ）品尝。</span></p>
<p><span style="word-wrap: break-word; white-space: normal; font-weight: 700; box-sizing: border-box; line-height: 25.2000007629395px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"><img src="http://7xotew.com1.z0.glb.clouddn.com/article-182-5.jpg" title="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_5" style="white-space: normal; float: none;" alt="日本札幌旅游攻略（美食篇）_图片_5"></span></p>
